summary:
Ready for the next step in my career. 

An open minded an ambitious young professional. 
After travelling and spending quite a long time abroad working as a cultural mediator, I had the opportunity to improve and perfect my adapting and interacting skills with cultures from all over de globe. 
Furthermore I have gained a lot of experience with customer service. 
This taught me how to overlook and foresee several demands and customer expectations. 
Finally a position as a team leader also allowed me to work on my communication and managing skills to several layers of employees and find solutions to any issue within the company in the best and most efficient way possible.
